"伊芙","body":"對啊！\n這個在多惠同學的黑髮上，\n我覺得是個很棒的點綴。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"伊芙，謝謝！\n那我下次Live就插著這個髮簪出場好了。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"啊，這條絲巾好像很適合薰學姊。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"真的耶！通透的紫色上頭\n還有小石閃耀，真的很漂亮。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"既然如此，這邊的項鍊就適合莉莎學姊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"選起適合大家的東西之後，\n就嗨起來了呢。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"對啊！只是像這樣四處逛，\n就開心到幾乎都要忘記時間了。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"這麼說來，我們做的東西，\n也是讓大家逛得這麼開心對吧。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"就是說啊。\n品項那麼豐富，大家都看得笑咪咪的。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"而且，大家也很開心地說\n多惠同學用紙黏土做的兔子，\n不管大的小的都很可愛喔！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"要這樣說，伊芙做的武士也很受歡迎啊。\n人家都說感覺得出來你很講究喔。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"真的嗎？\n我有努力挑戰真是太好了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"像這樣跟有著各種興趣的人接觸，\n真的很令人開心呢。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev93-ep5-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,